Package: potteR
Title: Analysis of Archaeological Pottery from Africa
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Nikolas", "Gestrich", , "gestrich@uni-frankfurt.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6376-1972"))
Description: This package provides functions for the analysis of archaeological ceramics from Africa. It is intended to build up to a complete analytical workflow for artefacts recorded following the system proposed by Jesse & Nowotnick (2022).  
